---
title: Scenario 11 — Multiple Rapid Transfers (Queue Ordering)
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant ParentVM as ParentViewModel
    participant Cache as SourceCache
    participant LeftBox as Left AnimatedListBox
    participant RightBox as Right AnimatedListBox
    participant Pipeline as Pipeline

    Note over LeftBox,RightBox: User clicks two items in rapid succession

    User->>ParentVM: Click Item A →
    ParentVM->>ParentVM: StampTransfer(A.id, ToSibling, FromSibling)
    ParentVM->>Cache: cache.Edit(A.IsOnRight = true)
    Cache-->>LeftBox: CollectionChanged (Remove A)
    Cache-->>RightBox: CollectionChanged (Add A)

    LeftBox->>Pipeline: Transfer A\njumps queue (idle)\n_pipelineBusy = true
    RightBox->>Pipeline: Transfer A\njumps queue (idle)\n_pipelineBusy = true

    Note over LeftBox,RightBox: A's slide animations start\n_inflightCount = 1 on each

    User->>ParentVM: Click Item B → (50ms later, during A's animation)
    ParentVM->>ParentVM: StampTransfer(B.id, ToSibling, FromSibling)
    ParentVM->>Cache: cache.Edit(B.IsOnRight = true)
    Cache-->>LeftBox: CollectionChanged (Remove B)
    Cache-->>RightBox: CollectionChanged (Add B)

    LeftBox->>LeftBox: ClassifyChange → Transfer\n_pipelineBusy = true → jump queue
    Note over LeftBox: SnapAllAnimations()\nA's animation snapped to final position\n_inflightCount = 0

    LeftBox->>Pipeline: _pipeline.Clear()\n_pipelineBusy = false
    LeftBox->>Pipeline: Enqueue Transfer B
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: TryProcessNext immediately\n_pipelineBusy = true

    RightBox->>RightBox: Same sequence for right side

    Note over LeftBox,RightBox: B's slide animations start\nA is already at rest (snapped)\nB animates cleanly

    Note over LeftBox,RightBox: B's animations complete\n_inflightCount = 0

    LeftBox->>Pipeline: OnAllAnimationsComplete\n_pipelineBusy = false
    RightBox->>Pipeline: OnAllAnimationsComplete\n_pipelineBusy = false

    Pipeline->>Pipeline: Queue empty — done

    Note over LeftBox,RightBox: Trade-off: A's animation was cut short\nbut B animates fully.\nTransfers always take priority.\nThis is the intended behaviour —\nthe most recent user action\nalways animates completely.
